{
  "page": "Blue Graces",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Blue Graces</b> are priestesses who provide healing in the religion of the <a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a>. Like other <a href=\"/index.php/Graces\" title=\"Graces\">Graces</a>, they dwell in the <a href=\"/index.php/Temple_of_the_Graces\" title=\"Temple of the Graces\">Temple of the Graces</a> of their city.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Known_Blue_Graces\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Blue Graces</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blue_Graces&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blue_Graces&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After the murder of <a href=\"/index.php/Stalwart_Shield\" title=\"Stalwart Shield\">Stalwart Shield</a>, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> gives an order to send men to the <a href=\"/index.php/Temple_of_the_Graces\" title=\"Temple of the Graces\">Temple of the Graces</a> to ask if any man has come to the Blue Graces with a sword wound.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Galazza_Galare\" title=\"Galazza Galare\">Galazza Galare</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace\" title=\"Green Grace\">Green Grace</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, returns to Daenerys, she is accompanied by three Blue Graces from the temple. They bring news of a sick and wounded rider who arrived on a pale horse. <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Worm\" title=\"Grey Worm\">Grey Worm</a> adds that he gave orders for the rider to be brought to the Blue Graces. One of the Blue Graces takes up the tale and tells Daenerys that the <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> brought the man to the temple, where they attended to him, though he died within the hour. A Blue Grace named <a href=\"/index.php/Ezzara\" title=\"Ezzara\">Ezzara</a> informs Daenerys that the man's fever was not brought on by the arrow in his thigh and that it may be that <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> has more to fear than the arrows of the <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a>'i.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As the <a href=\"/index.php/Bloody_flux\" title=\"Bloody flux\">bloody flux</a> known as the \"pale mare\" spreads, Daenerys sends healers, including Blue Graces, outside the walls of Meereen to aid the sick, but some of the healers sicken as well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After <a href=\"/index.php/Belwas\" title=\"Belwas\">Strong Belwas</a> is poisoned by eating <a href=\"/index.php/Poisoned_locusts\" title=\"Poisoned locusts\">honeyed locusts</a>, he is treated at the temple by Blue Graces.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Martell\" title=\"Quentyn Martell\">Quentyn Martell</a> is fatally wounded by <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegal\" title=\"Rhaegal\">Rhaegal</a>'s dragonflame, Barristan summons the Blue Graces four times to attend to Quentyn, but they never come. He wonders if the last of them have been carried off by the pale mare by now.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Blue_Graces\">Known Blue Graces</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blue_Graces&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Blue Graces\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ezzara\" title=\"Ezzara\">Ezzara</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blue_Graces&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Strong_Belwas\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Strong Belwas\">Strong Belwas</a> lingered at the door of death in <a href=\"/index.php/Temple_of_the_Graces\" title=\"Temple of the Graces\">the temple</a>, under the care of the Blue Graces ... though Selmy half suspected they were finishing the job those <a href=\"/index.php/Honeyed_locusts\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Honeyed locusts\">honeyed locusts</a> had begun.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blue_Graces&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_2\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 2\">Chapter 2</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 30\">Chapter 30</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Daenerys VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_55\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 55\">Chapter 55</a>, The Queensguard.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_59\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 59\">Chapter 59</a>, The Discarded Knight.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_70\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 70\">Chapter 70</a>, The Queen's Hand.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403195729\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.024 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.026 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 743/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8894/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3314/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 477/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3400/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   17.611      1 -total\n 77.20%   13.596      8 Template:Ref\n 47.71%    8.402      8 Template:Ref/core\n 15.89%    2.798      1 Template:References\n 12.83%    2.260      1 Template:Quote\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw